            <li>• Persistent fatigue and energy crashes</li>
            <li>• Mood swings and anxiety</li>
            <li>• Difficulty managing weight</li>
            <li>• Sleep disturbances</li>
            <li>• Brain fog and concentration issues</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Section 2: How Cold Exposure Affects Hormones -->
