        </p>

        <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-xl text-gray-800 mb-4">Cycle Syncing</h3>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Some women find it beneficial to adjust their cold plunging practice based on their menstrual cycle. During the follicular phase, you might tolerate longer or more frequent sessions, while during the luteal phase, shorter, gentler sessions may be preferable.
        </p>

        <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-xl text-gray-800 mb-4">Tracking Your Response</h3>
